(858, 'High & Low', 'Kirk Varnedoe, Adam Gopnik, Museum of Modern Art (New York, N.Y.)', 'comics', 10.64, 'http://books.google.com/books/content?id=T77pAAAAMAAJ&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&source=gbs_api', 'Readins in high & low'),
