(862, 'Drawing Now', 'Laura J. Hoptman, Museum of Modern Art (New York, N.Y.)', 'comics', 23.71, 'http://books.google.com/books/content?id=8KFjTa-A4jwC&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&edge=curl&source=gbs_api', 'Published to accompany the exhibition held at the Museum of Modern Art QNS, New York, 17 October 2002 - 6 January 2003.'),
