(1915, 'An Introduction to the Human Development and Capability Approach', 'Severine Deneulin, Lila Shahani', 'business', 13.60, 'http://books.google.com/books/content?id=kyRS_r-hfWoC&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&edge=curl&source=gbs_api', 'Since the publication of Nobel Laureate Amartya Sens flagship book \"Development as Freedom,\" development has been redefined in terms of human capability and opportunity. This approach has come to underpin the United Nations Development Programs influential Human Development Reports, and has had considerable significance in both academic and policy circles.'),
(1916, 'Doing Business with Serbia', 'Marat Terterov', 'business', 24.65, 'http://books.google.com/books/content?id=dduTMrBQxBsC&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&edge=curl&source=gbs_api', 'This second edition of Doing Business with Serbia is the definitive English language guide to investment potential, commercial opportunity and business practice in Serbia. The guide provides an objective and timely assessment of current economic climate, investment opportunities, and an insight into the rules of business engagement in Serbia\'s vibrant and fast moving economy. In addition, the guide will include detailed profiles of industry sectors and individual companies.'),
