(1967, 'The Magic School Bus Butterfly and the Bog Beast', 'Nancy E. Krulik, Joanna Cole', 'comics', 20.60, 'http://books.google.com/books/content?id=BqnOZERpxcEC&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&source=gbs_api', 'Ms. Frizzle\'s class has to come up with a mascot for its soccer team. Phoebe wants it to be a butterfly, but everyone else thinks that\'s a dumb idea...they\'re too wimpy! That\'s when know-it-all Janet suggests a bog beast mascot. The kids think it sounds realy cool. But just what is a bog beast? Find out when you join the class on an exciting field trip to a real live bog, where they learn all about bog beasts and butterflies.'),
